data.value: Hi! I'm Beatriz Varona, I'm an Astrophysicist. I work at the Astronomical Observatory of Teide, of the Instituto de Astrofísica de Canarias. I also worked at the Astronomical Observatory of Cantabria and CHARA Array in California.

I am Óscar Carrasco, a Computer Engineer from Tenerife, Spain. Although I am mostly specialized in systems engineering, my passion is hacking computers and having fun with both software and computers in general. I am often involved in open source projects and I'm always looking for new and exciting ideas to try!
